From 824fb19a16b2e65030f951c614c7ae6cf2d77930 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Marcello Sylvester Bauer <marcello.bauer@9elements.com>
Date: Thu, 8 Jan 2026 01:19:38 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 3/8] arm: gxp: add GXP peripheral drivers

Add peripheral drivers for the HPE GXP BMC SoC:

GPIO:
- gpio-gxp: GXP GPIO controller driver

I2C:
- i2c-gxp: GXP I2C bus controller
- I2C core updates for better OF and SMBus support

SPI:
- spi-gxp: GXP SPI controller driver
- gxp-spifi: GXP SPI Flash Interface (SPIFI) controller
- gxp-spifi-ctrl1: Secondary SPIFI controller

Serial:
- 8250_gxp_vuart: GXP Virtual UART driver for serial console

Network:
- gxp-umac: GXP Unified MAC Ethernet controller

MTD/Flash:
- Updates to Macronix and Winbond SPI-NOR drivers for GXP flash support

Signed-off-by: Marcello Sylvester Bauer <marcello.bauer@9elements.com>

